      "role": "user",
      "content": "wait, sorry, i didn't mean to sound like a novice lol. i just thought since st johns wort is herbal and natural it wouldn't be as harsh as meds. i've heard it works really well for mild cases. are you sure it's that dangerous? i feel like most people take supplements with their meds all the time without any issues.",
